content: 0xFlicker: Merged 3 bug fix PRs this month, including fixing a case sensitive issue in echogarden (#561), correcting a SQL command (#560), and passing runtime to the video service (#535). Made substantial code changes across 143 files (+9523/-9498 lines) in 8 commits, with a clear focus on bug fixes (88%) over feature work (13%). Has one open PR (#523) for adding services from plugins, showing sporadic activity on just 3 days this month.
